Choibasan (Dornod aimag; 61)<br>
Scorpion Co (gold company, part of Ministry of Geology)<br>
Lodoi Aiuur (President; in UB, h 33- 28-65, o/f 32-16-62)<br>
o 16-06, 13-56<br>
f 22-24<p>

Omnogov (South Gobi; 53)<br>
Baunguav TV. Bemsulen<br>
o 35-94<p>

Batsumber (100 km fm UB)<br>
Gomba TV. Nurgui, Aiumchimek (Nurgui's wife); with support of MNDP?<p>
</td></tr></table>
