drugsafelding GG&GD 1993:Amsterdam: GG&GD; 1994 
<li>Buster M. Centrale Methadone Registratie Jaarverlag 1993. Amsterdam: GG&GD 1994 
<li>van der Hoek JAR. Prevalence and risk factors of HIV' infections among drug users in 
Amsterdam. AIDS. 1988,2:55-60 
<li>van Amejden E. Evaluation of AIDS-prevention measures among drug users, the Amsterdam 
experience. Proeschrift UvA. 1994 
<li>van de Akker R, et al. Detection of HIV-antibody in Saliva as a tool for epidemiologic 
studies. AIDS, 1992,6:953-957 
<li>van Haastrecht HJA, et al. Estimating the size of the HIV epidemic among the i.v. drug 
users in Amsterdam. Submitted for publication. 1995 
<li>Terpstra MJH. Politieveldwerk, onbekende druggebruikers op Amsterdamse Politiebureau's 
Amsterdam: GG&GD; 1994</ol> 
<p>
<hr> 
<p> 
