flexibility in dosing (Rosenbaum 1985). On any 
methadone program, those clients who persist in using street drugs and produce dirty 
urine specimens are 
detoxified from the program regardless of their payment status. <a 
href="#back2">(Back)</a> 
<a name="note3"></a><li>More clients were expected to go to other counties for both 
detoxification and maintenance treatment. 
