<center><h2>
A Selected Bibliography on Alcohol Control,<br>
Particularly before and at Repeal</h2></center>
<p>
<font size=2><i>
Levine, Harry Gene, and David C. Smith, comp.<br>
<b>A Selected Bibliography on Alcohol Control,<br>
Particularly before and at Repeal.</b>  California:<br>
University of California, Berkeley, 1977.
</i></font size=2>
