Epidemiological and Clinical Perspectives, ed. Nicholas J. Kozel and Edgar H. Adams, 
National Institute of Drug Abuse Research Monograph 61 (Washington, D.C., GPO, 
1985), 73. 
<li>Lester Grinspoon and James B. Bakalar, Psychedelic Drugs Reconsidered (New York: 
Basic Books, 1979), 157-191. 
